data.description: Highly sought after location of Port Saint Lucie's Sandpiper Bay. Tucked in just off Morningside Blvd, South of Port Saint Lucie Blvd. West of U.S. 1 Close to everything possibly needed. End of street unit with no buildings to the west.  One Bedroom and one Bathroom on fist level. 2 bedrooms 1 bath upstairs.  Great square footage with great value.  24 X 21 Fully Screened Entry Patio that creates an amazing tropical feel with private exterior space. Sliding glass doors that allows natural light all year and amazing winter breezes with larger open feel. This is a must see in person to make your own. New Sliding Glass Door and Window for first level bedroom
